column5:
23 pages, this improves and generalizes some results in
  arXiv:1012.3818; v2, abstract is modified, and Cor. 1 and 3.4-5 are added;
  v3, Remark 3.6 added

10 pages, 3 figure, IOP style; version2: one reference corrected;
  version 3 (final version for JSTAT): some minor typos and citation errors
  fixed

19 pages; Journal of Functional Analysis, accepted for publication; a
  better presentation of certain parts; minor corrections and modifications;
  references and thanks were added
